main event: A UFO was observed near Miamisburg, Ohio, on 27 November 1957, traveling in a tumbling motion.
interesting points: The object was observed for a duration of 3 minutes., The object was described as very dark, traveling from the NE to the SSW., It was located about 5 kilometers northeast of the observer., The movement of the object appeared to be tumbling end over end., The report lacks sufficient information for a conclusive identification of the object.
